jb hm esy likhengy to wo jitni total yani jitna parent he jesy parent 100px  he to wo phly 100 sy  ko gap  - kryga or gap he 10 to wo 90 ho jayga or phir jitny fr hongy 4 5 osko divide krdega or jo ayga number to wo jesy 25 to wo 25px ke hisab sy wirdh de dega

or agr hm likhen kisi fr ki jha auto grid-template-column :auto 1fr 1fr 1fr  to wo iski w lekr ayga parent sy or agr parent ke pas jo w or border agr hoga ya koch esi chiz jo jga leti hon osko + krky jo w bany gi  wo  w dedega colom ko jesy parent ke pas he 10 to wo 10 w rakhyga column ki or osky bad 100 me sy kryga - 10 bavhy ga 90 to wo 90 ko divide kryga baki bachy 3 sy auto ko hta kr or on
3 ko de dega osky hisab sy w devide krky bachi  hoi value ko 

or agr parent kepas w nhi he to wo border jitna hga otni jga lega agr wo bhi nhi he to wo auto ko milayga hi nhi kisi chiz me samjhyga bs 3 card hen

isi trha jb hmny likha ho 1fr 1fr 2fr 3fr iska matlb ye howa ke total hmary pas he 7fr lekin hen 4 hi srif w ke liye wo 7 hen yani wo divide kryga 100 ko 7 sy or  phir jesy 25 ans aya to wo phly me 1fr he to osko 25 w dega or 2 me bhi 1fr he to osko bhi 25 dega lekin 3 me kioky 2fr he to yani 50 w milygi 3 or 4 ko pr column hongy 4 hi

50fr 1fr 2fr 3fr agr hm esy dety hen to wo 100 sy 50 ko - kryga than wo 10 gap nikaly ga phir 40 ko 3 sy divide kryga


