gridcolomn: "span 2"
iska matlb span 2 yani phly 2 card ko marge krdo yani 110 mesy - gap 10 ka to phir bachyga 100 phir 100 ko 4 sy devide 25 to 3 colom bnygy ak 50 kioky span 2 ka matlb phky 2 ko marge krlo lekin agr phla auto he or na w he parent ke pas na border to wo 3 hi lega or equl krdyga 

or parent matlb jisky ander card he ya koch bhi parant wo nhi he jismy hm colom bnary jis div me hm colon bnary wo wo khod he jismy div he wo parent he